      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">LADIES ¶ ' ¶ LEICHARDT ¶ Leichhardt's name mis-spelled in the printed letterhead. ¶ SEARCH ¶ COMMITTEE ¶ 28/6/65...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.06.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Branwhite<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Clarke</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">DL MS Q371, pp. 141-4, W. B. Clarke papers,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dixson<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Library, State Library of New South Wales.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">The transcription given</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in Moyal (2003), pp. 708-9</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">, differs from that given here</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">LADIES</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">'</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">LEICHARDT</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Leichhardt's name mis-spelled in the printed letterhead.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">SEARCH</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">COMMITTEE</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28/6/65</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Reverend and venerable friend,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your letter just arrived is certainly so admirable, that with consent of the Ladies Committe I have the main portion of it transferred to the "Australasian,"<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See W. B. Clarke to M, 20 June 1865.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>trusting that you will not disapprove<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the step. It is but just that your noble exertions should be fully known, especially as I have in my speech at St George's Hall<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B65.02.01, subsequently widely reprinted.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not done justice to you. This apparent shortcoming arose from the fact, that only a few months before I had in the report on the graves found<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Conn<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp; Giles,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">William Conn and Ernest Giles.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>referred to some extent to your exertions &amp; your opinions.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B65.14.05,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">a copy of which was sent to Augustus Gregory<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">to obtain his opinion as to the further investigation concerning Leichhardt</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">s fate</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(resolution at the meeting of the Royal Society of Victoria, 10 October 1864 after M had read the report,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions and proceedings of the Royal Society<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">of</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Victoria</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">, <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>vol</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>6, p. lii).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The only copy I had of your long printed letter,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'Leichhardt and the Desert',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Sydney morning herald</seg>, 24 August 1858, pp. 4-5.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in which you weigh so fully the evidence I sent with our report to Mr Gregory &amp; have had no oppurtunity of restoring it. The report is however printed in the new volume of our Royal Society &amp; thus my appreciation of your exertions<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>permanently<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>recorded.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mrs Dr Bromby has secured the cooperation of Prof Pell, a friend of her brother. I trust you will unite with the few, who now uphold conjointly your friend's claims.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sundry articles in the Melbourne papers will show what progress is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>made. Pardon me for the briefness &amp;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>inelegance<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of this note. I write hurriedly amidst other<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>engagements.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May you enjoy the blessings of health &amp; contentedness, that is the wish of your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>attached</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
